DA Federal Congress 2020 JOHANNESBURG - The race for a new leader of the Democratic Alliance is on. The party is holding its two-day virtual leadership conference. READ: DA leadership race heats up The party's interim leader, John Steenhuisen and Mbali Ntuli will face off for the leadership position. Meanwhile, Hellen Zille is fighting to retain her position as Federal Chairperson against, Mike Moriarty.